&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Airbnb&#39;s Creative team is composed of marketing and creative talent who serve as the company&#39;s storytellers — responsible for sharing Airbnb&#39;s vision and product promise with hosts and guests around the world. Our work spans campaigns, social, product launches, and product marketing, all grounded in Airbnb&#39;s core values. As Creative Lead, Photo, you&#39;ll sit at the intersection of brand and craft, partnering closely with cross-functional teams including Marketing, Product, and external agencies to bring Airbnb&#39;s visual identity to life at a global scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Creative Lead, Photo, you will own the photographic creative vision for Airbnb — leading a talented team of Photo Art Directors, Editors, Retouchers, and Researchers to produce world-class imagery that authentically represents the Airbnb brand. You will be the creative force that elevates the quality and consistency of photo-driven storytelling across all channels and touchpoints. Success in this role means delivering a cohesive, culturally resonant visual language that measurably strengthens brand perception and supports business outcomes across campaigns, product launches, and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead and mentor&lt;/strong&gt; a team of Photo Art Directors, Editors, Retouchers, and Researchers — providing clear creative direction, ongoing feedback, and fostering an environment where individuals are empowered to do their best work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Concept and develop&lt;/strong&gt; strategically informed, channel-agnostic photo ideas that are deeply integrated across all brand and product touchpoints, from campaign to social to product marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Oversee and art direct&lt;/strong&gt; photo shoots end-to-end, ensuring all deliverables align with the strategic brief, Airbnb&#39;s visual identity, and overall brand intention&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uplevel creative output&lt;/strong&gt; across the organization by consistently bringing innovative, high-impact ideas to the table and setting a high bar for craft and authenticity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally&lt;/strong&gt; with a diverse mix of internal teams — including Marketing, Product, and Brand — as well as external agencies and international partners, balancing stakeholder needs while always seeking to elevate the work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communicate and align&lt;/strong&gt; with creative teammates and company partners to ensure Airbnb&#39;s photo-driven creative work maintains the highest standard of quality and consistency across global markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10+ years&lt;/strong&gt; of art and creative direction experience within an agency or in-house brand environment, with demonstrated experience working with global companies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strong portfolio showcasing your ability to lead teams in creating photography-driven communication campaigns that resonate culturally and drive measurable business results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep expertise in &lt;strong&gt;Photo Art Direction as a storytelling tool&lt;/strong&gt; — with a nuanced understanding of how photography communicates brand narrative both in marketing and within product experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven &lt;strong&gt;people leadership and management skills&lt;/strong&gt;, with experience inspiring and empowering creative teams through a strong, clear vision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional &lt;strong&gt;communication and presentation skills&lt;/strong&gt;, with the ability to passionately and clearly articulate and defend creative decisions to internal stakeholders and external partners alike&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outstanding &lt;strong&gt;cross-functional collaboration skills&lt;/strong&gt;, with a track record of establishing and meeting shared, outcome-based goals across diverse teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in &lt;strong&gt;Figma&lt;/strong&gt; is required; comfort working within collaborative, tool-driven creative workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or equivalent combination of education and progressive experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
