&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;The Process and Strategy Optimization (PSO) team within Fraud and Safety Operations supports the broader mission of protecting Airbnb’s community and strengthening trust across the platform. We strive for seamless delivery of new defenses and enhancements that protect users, scale efficiently, and deliver a world-class experience. Our work ensures solutions are innovative, scalable, and operationally sound, enabling teams to deliver on Airbnb’s promise of safety and trust.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
