&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The communications team is responsible for telling the Airbnb story around the world. Whether we are briefing press on inspiring travel trends, highlighting unique experiences led by local hosts, or explaining how travel on our platform benefits local families and communities, we are the voice of Airbnb on a broad range of topics.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a fast-growing and high-energy team with a passion for people, places and great stories. If you&#39;d like to be part of one of the world&#39;s greatest communications teams, come tell us your story.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are hiring a Senior Consumer Communications Manager to tell the Airbnb story in Germany. This role is responsible for delivering large-scale consumer-facing campaigns while ensuring a regular press-office drumbeat of stories and news aimed at driving awareness and consideration of Airbnb across the country.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will collaborate closely with cross-functional partners to ensure Airbnb remains a key player in consumer-facing media. They will also support the company’s reputation by sharing our story with a diverse audience of journalists, influencers, and community members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking a creative communications professional with a proven track record of developing and executing consumer communications initiatives that generate widespread awareness and brand buzz. The ideal candidate has a deep understanding of popular culture, a passion for storytelling, and thrives in an entrepreneurial environment, managing multiple projects and priorities effectively.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role is based in Germany and reports to the Communications Lead, DACH &amp;amp; CEE.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate global communications priorities into locally nuanced ideas that support Airbnb’s key business objectives in the local market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify proactive press opportunities and drive national/global announcements, in support of consumer and product goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop campaigns or programs that resonate with Italian audiences to help drive demand for Airbnb, involving key partners, celebrities,&amp;nbsp; influencers or opinion leaders in Germany&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle incoming media inquiries, leveraging tools such as data, industry research, and host &amp;amp; guest stories to support Airbnb&#39;s community and brand&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with local, regional, and global Communications team members, as well as key cross-functional business stakeholders, to ensure a coordinated and strategic approach to communications initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Liaise with our host &amp;amp; guest community over media opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop written materials (press releases, blog posts, story pitches, Q&amp;amp;As, briefs, messaging guidelines, presentations etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage relationships with key reporters and celebrities/ influencers across Italy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help manage a local agency and ensure key processes are adhered to, including campaign project management, coverage reporting, press office calendar management and the localization of key global press materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of comprehensive communications experience, either in a PR agency or an in-house communications team. Previous experience in high-performing international organizations within entertainment, tech,&amp;nbsp; or travel sectors is a plus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s Degree, german native speaker, fluent in English with excellent writing and verbal communications skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven-track record of developing and executing creative consumer communications initiatives that generate positive earned media coverage, widespread awareness, and brand buzz&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong awareness of pop culture and the ability to craft ideas that drive editorial media coverage and social engagement, tailoring communications efforts to resonate with diverse audiences&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to create a strong editorial plan that ensure a constant media drumbeat combining global stories and local stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at originating, project managing, and delivering complex, proactive press projects, ranging from research/data-driven stories and campaigns to press events, press trips, and celebrity/influencer engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adept at collaborating with multi-functional teams in a matrix organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confident in leading meetings with external partners, senior stakeholders and media contacts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in working with celebrities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about Airbnb and the mission of the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in agency management, including briefing, budget and impact analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment and adapting flexibly to change&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment To Inclusion &amp;amp; Belonging:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Airbnb is committed to working with the broadest talent pool possible. We believe diverse ideas foster innovation and engagement, and allow us to attract creatively-led people, and to develop the best products, services and solutions. All qualified individuals are encouraged to apply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;How We&#39;ll Take Care of You:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The actual base pay is dependent upon many factors, such as: training, transferable skills, work experience, business needs and market demands. The base pay range shown below is annualized, is subject to change and may be modified in the future. This role may also be eligible for bonus, benefits, and Employee Travel Credits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Germany Annual Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;€84.000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;€105.000 EUR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you passionate about driving the success of a global business in the dynamic and fast-paced world of corporate communications? If so, we have the perfect opportunity for you!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Corporate Communications Manager for France, you will play a central role in shaping and executing the communications strategy for one of the biggest markets for Airbnb globally. The ideal candidate is a self-starter and a team player who is deeply immersed in the media landscape, not just in France, but also has a global perspective, and who can manage complex media relationships, shape narrative, and navigate challenging communications landscapes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joining our French Communications team based in our vibrant Paris office, you will have the chance to work closely with the local policy, business, marketing, and the regional communications team, forging strong partnerships and ensuring a positive reputation and favorability for Airbnb in the French market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You Will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not your average Corporate Communications role. You will have the opportunity to drive impactful projects and campaigns, manage a busy press office, and engage directly with journalists. With your established media contacts in France, you will be at the forefront of shaping the narrative and telling Airbnb&#39;s story in France.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your work will be diverse and exciting, from managing media inquiries and coordinating high-profile events to gathering compelling stories from our amazing community of hosts. You will have the freedom to develop and deliver innovative communications plans that showcase the benefits of sharing your home and traveling on Airbnb while providing strategic counsel to top senior leadership.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you thrive in a fast-paced environment, love building relationships, and have a passion for driving positive change, this role is made for you. Join us in shaping the future of Airbnb&#39;s corporate and policy communications in the French market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is based in Paris (hybrid, 2-3 days a week in the office) and is a 12-month fixed-term contract.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with the French team to develop robust and effective corporate and policy communications strategies and implement them&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the press office and handle all reactive Corporate &amp;amp; Policy enquiries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop relationships with key reporters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help draft written materials - story pitches, press releases, messaging guidelines, Q&amp;amp;As, briefs, presentations, speeches, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create monthly coverage reports, evaluating and measuring coverage impact&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support with briefings for media interviews and public speaking engagements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6-8 years experience working in policy and corporate communications in an agency, in-house or in high level public administrations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working on communications initiatives involving trust, crisis, policy, regulatory, corporate and financial matters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have an expert knowledge of the challenging and compelling French media landscape&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work collaboratively with multi-functional leads in a matrix organisation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent English &amp;amp; French, spoken and written&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent writing and strong verbal communications and interpersonal skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in media relations with an established media network in France&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working on projects in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining enthusiasm and a calm demeanor in stressful situations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for Airbnb and the mission of the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team spirit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Commitment To Inclusion &amp;amp; Belonging:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Airbnb is committed to working with the broadest talent pool possible. We believe diverse ideas foster innovation and engagement, and allow us to attract creatively-led people, and to develop the best products, services and solutions. All qualified individuals are encouraged to apply.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;description&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;How We&#39;ll Take Care of You:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The actual base pay is dependent upon many factors, such as: training, transferable skills, work experience, business needs and market demands. The base pay range shown below is annualized, is subject to change and may be modified in the future. This role may also be eligible for bonus, benefits, and Employee Travel Credits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;France Annual Pay Range&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;€74.000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;€93.000 EUR&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Airbnb was born in 2007 when two hosts welcomed three guests to their San Francisco home, and has since grown to over 5 million hosts who have welcomed over 2 billion guest arrivals in almost every country across the globe. Every day, hosts offer unique stays and experiences that make it possible for guests to connect with communities in a more authentic way.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Community You Will Join:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Are you passionate about driving the success of a global business in the dynamic, evolving, and fast-paced world of corporate and policy communications?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;As the Senior Corporate and Policy Communications Manager for DACH &amp;amp; CEE, you will play a central role in shaping and executing the communications strategy for one of our most important European markets. You will help tell Airbnb&#39;s story - how we build trust and belonging in communities—while navigating one of Europe&#39;s most complex regulatory landscapes.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Joining our DACH &amp;amp; CEE Communications team based in Berlin, you will work closely with local policy, marketing, legal, and partnerships teams, and forge strong relationships across EMEA and the US. Your role is critical: Germany&#39;s regulatory environment around housing, short-term rentals, and overtourism is complex and politically sensitive and your ability to shape and amplify impactful narratives, anticipate issues, and maintain Airbnb&#39;s reputation will directly influence business outcomes and regulatory relationships.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Difference You will Make:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Drive impactful campaigns addressing overtourism challenges through locally relevant nature tourism and travel dispersal narratives, positioning Airbnb as a responsible community actor that builds trust and belonging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Manage the press office across complex topics: regulatory affairs, housing policy, taxation, community impact, and trust &amp;amp; safety&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Engage directly with journalists in Germany; build and leverage established media contacts to shape narrative and anticipate emerging threats&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Work with cross functional partners to develop, plan and execute a regular drumbeat of robust stories and comms moments that demonstrate Airbnb&#39;s contribution to communities and economies while navigating sensitive regulatory terrain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Lead agency partnerships, setting strategic direction for external communications suppliers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Protect the business by proactively communicating our commitment to community trust, responsible hosting, and addressing legitimate policy concern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;If you thrive in fast-paced environments with a focus on execution, have a strong nose for a good story, and can balance strategic thinking with hands-on crisis management while championing our mission to build trust and belonging, this role is for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Typical Day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develop proactive corporate and policy communications strategy with Germany Policy, Legal, Marketing, and Partnerships teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Manage the press office, handling reactive media enquiries and responding to journalists on deadline with strategic messaging&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Build relationships with key reporters and editors in the German media landscape; identify proactive story opportunities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Develop written communications materials (story pitches, press releases, messaging, Q&amp;amp;As, briefs, presentations)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Brief executives and colleagues for media interviews and public speaking engagements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Lead agency partnerships and manage external communications suppliers&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Monitor the news cycle to identify emerging threats and opportunities for proactive communications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with Policy, Legal, Consumer Communications, and global corporate communications teams&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
