&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As a Staff Experience Designer, you will partner with supporting disciplines such as writers, researchers, product specialists and engineers to build beautiful, usable, forward-looking products that empower people. Our design charter is to help foster an emotional connection with our community, keeping usability and accessibility as our prime virtues. We do our best to practice inclusive design at every turn, spanning both the online and offline experiences we create for our community.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
