&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Partner with Product Managers, Engineers, Data Scientist, Researchers and Writers to define problems &amp;amp; goals, map user flows, prototype interactions, and launch new products and services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
